    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, delivering linear power delivery through its 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal, ensuring the integrity of the intermediate shaft assembly. The throttle response is sharp, characteristic of the VarioCam Plus variable valve timing system. While the exterior shows minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the aerodynamic profile remains uncompromised. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated rotors, providing exceptional thermal dissipation. A mechanically robust example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
