    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been meticulously curated for the driver who demands both mechanical integrity and refined aesthetics. Demonstrating a history of conscientious ownership, it remains in commendable condition, offering a seamless and reliable driving experience. Our rigorous multi-point inspection confirms its readiness for the road, ensuring that every system operates with the precision expected of a high-caliber motorcar. This represents a premier opportunity to secure a sophisticated vehicle that balances enduring performance with exceptional value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
