      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It is the perfect daily driver for someone who wants something reliable that still looks great in the driveway. I've taken great care of it, so it's all ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
