    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an E46 M3 equipped with the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The vehicle exhibits sharp throttle response and maintains excellent lateral stability through its multi-link rear suspension. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including VANOS servicing and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for this chassis. While the exterior shows minor road wear, the mechanical vitals are strong, making this a tactile, analog performer ready for the twisties.",
